Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese Tea ceremony is an activity that cultivate moral character and develop temperament by making tea ,appreciating  tea and drinking tea . \N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,let me show you how to make a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should prepare the tea set,it includes the tea tray,tea cup,teapot,tea leaves,the cylinder of teaspoon and the boiling water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly,burning the teapot and the tea cup with boiling water. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It can clean them and make the musty taste  disappear.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly,using a tea spoon to fill the teapot one fifth to a half full with tea leaves . 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pouring water into the teapot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first pass is to be drained of water. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is washing tea. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Washing tea needs to be finished quickly, because it only needs to wake up the fragrance of tea.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirdly,if it has bubbles on the surface of the tea. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t stop injecting water 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,until it nearly overflow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then we can scrape bubbles  with the lid.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After washing tea , we pour boiling water  highly  on the teapot. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Covering with the lid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Drenching the teapot with boiling water, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be better if we can do it for three times. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because high temperature inside and outside can make you smell the fragrance of tea .\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally,we can pour the tea into the tea cup. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we can enjoy the good tea,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After using the teapot, we should wash it and sidelong the lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t  screw down the lid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should put the teapot in the dry place ,but avoiding the chemical agent.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't often pour water into the teapot, unless we brew with tea.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the simulation of Chinese tea ceremony.Thank you!
